<div class="banner" id="home-banner">
  <div class="darken">
    <h1 class="white" id="home-title"> <%= t ".headline" %> </h1>
    <p class="white" id="home-subtitle">We are UC Berkeley students who want to use technology to improve our community.</p>
    <div id="laptop">
      <div id="laptop-content-container">
        <%= image_tag("home/laptop-content.png", id:"laptop-content") %>
      </div>
      <div id="laptop-bg-container">
        <%= image_tag("home/macbook-bg.png", id:"laptop-bg") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="spacer"></div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-9 large-7 small-centered columns center">
    <h1>What We Do</h1>
    <div class="spacer-small"></div>
    <p> Blueprint is a student organization aimed at using technology for social good.
        We build websites and mobile applications for nonprofits for free. We also put on multiple
        events a year highlighting nonprofits using technology in creative ways and disucssions on
        how to use technology to promote public welfare. </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="spacer"></div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="medium-5 small-12 columns center">
    <div id="smartphone-content-container">
      <%= image_tag("home/smartphone-content.png", id:"smartphone-content") %>
    </div>
    <div id="smartphone-bg-container">
      <%= image_tag("home/smartphone-bg.png", id:"smartphone-bg") %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="medium-6 medium-offset-1 small-12 columns center" id="#our-projects">
    <div class="spacer-large"></div>
    <h1>Our Projects</h1>
    <p> Blueprint is a non-profit organization aimed at bringing technologies to local nonprofit organizations that are making social change. Each year, teams of five students work with non-profit organizations to implement technologies like some of these application below: </p>
    <%= link_to "See More Work", projects_path, class:"button" %>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="spacer-large"></div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-9 small-centered columns center">
    <h1>Our Events</h1>
    <p> We host multiple events a year to promote tech for social good and support company
        recruiting. We frequently hold fireside chats and panels with nonprofit and technology
        leaders. We have also hold tech talks and info sessions with a number of different companies.
    </p>
    <div class="spacer-small"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-9 small-centered columns center">
    <ul class="small-block-grid-3">
      <li><img src="http://goo.gl/EXVuUJ"></li>
      <li><img src="http://goo.gl/lrqEJC"></li>
      <li><img src="http://goo.gl/5sNrte"></li>
    </ul>
    <%= link_to "All Events", projects_path, class:"button" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="spacer"></div>
<div class="gray-bg">
  <div class="spacer"></div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="medium-8 small-12 columns small-centered center">
      <h1>Get Involved</h1>
      <p>Are you a nonprofit looking to partner? Are you a student looking to join? Be sure to check out the links below
         to find out how you can get involved in bringing technology to social good! Please do not hesitate to contact
         us with any questions. </p>
      <%= link_to "For Nonprofits", nonprofits_apply_path, class: "button" %>
      <%= link_to "For Students", students_apply_path, class: "button" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="spacer-large"></div>
</div>
